summary:
Just a simple retexture I did for one of my characters. Replaces the item "Tavern Clothes".
Based on the outfit of Nora Valkyrie from "RWBY".
descriptionHtml:
Just a simple retexture I did for one of my characters. Replaces the item "Tavern Clothes".
Based on the outfit of Nora Valkyrie from "RWBY". To get the item ingame open up the console input [quote]help "tavern clothes" [/quote]and then player.additem (The ID your console gives after using the first command).
